songs.title: Like The Other Girls
songs.lyrics:
You think I'm like the other girls
You think I'm like the rest
You think I'd like to rule the world
But this is all a test

Hey! You think you're seeing the future
Hey! You think the feeling is mutual

You think I'm like the other girls
You think I'm like the rest
You think I'd like to rule the world
But this is all a test

Ooh...

Hey! Thinking you want domination
Hey! You're not a teenage sensation
Hey! I'll wipe that sunburn away
Hey! Won't give a fuck what you say

Ooh...
